TITLE: Creating Multi-Step AI Workflow with Inngest in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet illustrates a complex AI workflow using Inngest's multi-step functions. It chains together calls to OpenAI, Hugging Face, and Anthropic APIs, demonstrating how to enhance reliability and manage costs in AI-powered applications.
