TITLE: Configuring Event Batching in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Creates an Inngest function that processes batches of events with TypeScript. The function is configured with a maximum batch size, timeout, and optional key for grouping events by user ID. It maps event data and performs a bulk database write operation.
