TITLE: Creating an Autonomous Agent Network with AgentKit
DESCRIPTION: Implements a network that runs a coding agent in a loop until it completes its goal. The network is configured with a maximum of 10 iterations and uses a defaultRouter function to determine when to stop execution based on a task_summary key in the state.
