SOURCE: https://github.com/inngest/website/blob/main/content/blog/debouncing-in-queuing-systems-optimizing-efficiency-in-async-workflows.mdx#2025-04-10_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
CREATE TABLE debounce_job_queue (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  job_type VARCHAR(64),
  status VARCHAR(64),
  payload JSONB,
  scheduled_at TIMESTAMP,
  debounce_key VARCHAR(64)
);
```

